# CTS-prodigi-project
Submition for CTS prodigi (KooVerse)

Team members: Soubhik Pailan , Itasha Modi, Sagar Dutta , Parthiv Konwer, Jayshree Karmakar
             
Our idea: A Cardano blockchain based Metaverse accessible through all platform whether Windows, Android, Web, AR or VR. 

Similar projects in existence: There are a few Cardano based metaverse in existence including CARDALONIA METAVERSE, PAVIA METAVERSE, REACH METAVERSE, VIRTUA METAVERSE.

Uniqueness: There are no Cardano Metaverses to our knowledge that has the same target audience as us(school and college students). 

              
              
              
